data.text:
Liv Tyler says the years since her split from husband Royston Langdon have been a struggle, but she’s been “rebuilding” her life. Liv told Bust magazine that 6-year-old son, Milo, is her priority. “I just had a rough couple of years, having Milo and then getting divorced and trying to rebuild my life again,” she said. She’ll next appear in flicks “Super” and “The Ledge.”

Originally Published: March 27, 2011 at 12:00 a.m.
